URL->View->HTML
Create a branch named <yourName+week21>
Edit this file and write the commands to create a new project

1. Write Commands to create a django project
    1. activate virtual env
    2. django-admin startproject [project_name]

    ...
2. Write Commands to create django app
    1. cd <project_name>
    2. mkdir apps
    3. cd apps
    4. make __init__.py file
    5. python ../manage.py startapp [app_name]

    ...
DONT FORGET FOLDERS AND URLS!
    1. update settings
    2. update url
ALL SUDO CODE! Don't run the commands!

3. Start on Ninja Gold

Add URL, then work on view, then HTML or redirect

